						<p>Check out this <a href="http://dw.cbsi.com/redir?tag=medccnbwp&siteId=2&ptid=8301&onid=800023&q=&ctype=docids&cval=32913453&destUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.techrepublic.com%2Fresource-library%2Fwhitepapers%2Ften-smart-things-to-know-about-storage%2F%3Fpromo%3D999516%26cval%3Dwhitepapers">white paper</a> to learn about trends, developments and tips to make your <a href="http://dw.cbsi.com/redir?tag=medccnbwp&siteId=2&ptid=8301&onid=800023&q=&ctype=docids&cval=32913453&destUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.techrepublic.com%2Fresource-library%2Fwhitepapers%2Ften-smart-things-to-know-about-storage%2F%3Fpromo%3D999516%26cval%3Dwhitepapers">storage environment</a> more efficient.</p>
